snippet.title: Blood 2 Gameplay
snippet.description:
To watch this vid in HD press this http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OTNY_TQZOXA&fmt=18

-----------------

This was recorded with fraps and played by me.Blood 2 was a game made by monolith that used the Lith engine (Shogo MAD used that to). The game is pretty fun i recommend not only getting this game but also getting the nightmare levels
